<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Job Offer Letter</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 40px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .company-name {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .letter-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 30px 0 20px 0;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .employee-info {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 50px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .signature-box {
            width: 45%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .signature-line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
            margin: 40px 0 10px 0;
        }
        .date {
            text-align: right;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="company-name">{{company.name}}</div>
        <div>{{company.address}}</div>
        <div>Phone: {{company.phone}} | Email: {{company.email}}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="date">
        <strong>Date:</strong> {{employee.current_date}}
    </div>

    <div class="greeting">
        Dear {{employee.full_name}},
    </div>

    <div class="letter-title">JOB OFFER LETTER</div>

    <p>We are pleased to offer you the position of <strong>{{employee.job_title}}</strong> in our {{employee.department_name}} department. We believe your skills and experience will be a valuable addition to our team.</p>

    <div class="employee-info">
        <strong>Position Details:</strong><br>
        Job Title: {{employee.job_title}}<br>
        Department: {{employee.department_name}}<br>
        Start Date: {{employee.formatted_hire_date}}<br>
        Salary: {{employee.formatted_salary}} per month<br>
        Employee Code: {{employee.employee_code}}
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Terms and Conditions</div>
        <p>This offer is subject to the following terms and conditions:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>You will report to the Department Manager</li>
            <li>Your normal working hours will be 9:00 AM to 5:00 PM, Monday through Friday</li>
            <li>You will be entitled to all benefits as per company policy</li>
            <li>This offer is valid for 7 days from the date of this letter</li>
            <li>Your employment will be subject to a probationary period of 3 months</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Next Steps</div>
        <p>To accept this offer, please:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Sign and return this letter within 7 days</li>
            <li>Complete the required documentation</li>
            <li>Attend the orientation session on your start date</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <p>We look forward to welcoming you to our team. If you have any questions about this offer, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>

    <p>Congratulations on your new position!</p>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="signature-box">
            <div class="signature-line"></div>
            <div><strong>Employee Signature</strong></div>
            <div>{{employee.full_name}}</div>
            <div>Date: _______________</div>
        </div>
        <div class="signature-box">
            <div class="signature-line"></div>
            <div><strong>HR Manager</strong></div>
            <div>{{company.name}}</div>
            <div>Date: _______________</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
